INSERT INTO `article` VALUES (1, '徐州出行须知！行前看这篇就够了', '说起徐州，很多人可能会“误会”它是山东的“一份子”，其实，它身处“苏北”，是妥妥的江苏er。\r\n地处苏、皖、鲁、豫四省交界的徐州，可以说是江苏省最特别的城市，虽然在江苏，但在秦岭淮河以北，是一个童叟无欺、货真价实的每逢冬天，作为江苏省唯一有“暖气福利”的城市，可真让省内其他兄弟城市羡慕坏了。', 'http://localhost:8080/files/download/44.jpeg', '<div class=\"_j_content\">\r\n                                                        <div class=\"f-block\" id=\"_j_paragraph_1\"><h2>初识徐州</h2></div>\r\n                    \r\n\r\n                        <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                <div class=\"p-section\">\r\n                    说起徐州，很多人可能会“误会”它是山东的“一份子”，其实，它身处“苏北”，是妥妥的江苏er。<br>\r\n<br>\r\n地处苏、皖、鲁、豫四省交界的徐州，可以说是江苏省<b>最特别</b>的城市，虽然在江苏，但在秦岭淮河以北，是一个童叟无欺、货真价实的<b>北方城市。</b>每逢冬天，作为江苏省唯一有“暖气福利”的城市，可真让省内其他兄弟城市羡慕坏了。\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        \r\n\r\n                        <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"height: 532px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/b1/fd/fabb7d4ce451b91cda67b6acc668e598.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/b1/fd/fabb7d4ce451b91cda67b6acc668e598.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/b1/fd/fabb7d4ce451b91cda67b6acc668e598.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\">\r\n                <span class=\"img-an\">\r\n                                            \r\n                                    </span>\r\n            </div>\r\n        \r\n\r\n                        <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                <div class=\"p-section\">\r\n                    也因此，徐州的魅力也是独特的。她比南方多了一种雄浑气韵，又比北方多了一些清秀温婉。走在大街小巷，你可能听不到什么吴侬软语，倒是能听到不少“俺”、“管”等北方用词，让安徽、河南和山东的朋友都能感受到“宾至如归”。<br>\r\n<br>\r\n然而更让人惊喜的是，徐州是华夏九州之一，厚重的历史便是这座城市最为人称道的事儿。这里自古便是兵家必争之地，一次次浴火重生，从原始社会到近现代，都留下了大量人文古迹值得探寻。\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        \r\n\r\n                        <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"height: 509px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s14/M00/75/FC/wKgE2l0i48mAWLX-ABLeT5pAu1Q713.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s14/M00/75/FC/wKgE2l0i48mAWLX-ABLeT5pAu1Q713.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s14/M00/75/FC/wKgE2l0i48mAWLX-ABLeT5pAu1Q713.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\">\r\n                <span class=\"img-an\">\r\n                                             by 不冷静小姐奇遇记\r\n                                    </span>\r\n            </div>\r\n        \r\n\r\n                        <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                <div class=\"p-section\">\r\n                    如果真想了解徐州，还是得亲自好好玩一趟：清晨登上<b>云龙山</b>，俯瞰<b>云龙湖和徐州城</b>；白日漫步<b>户部山古建筑群</b>，寻找昔日家族兴旺的欢声笑语；打卡<b>汉墓</b>和<b>徐州博物馆</b>，感受历史的岁月变迁。\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        \r\n\r\n                        <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                <section class=\"travelnote\">\r\n                    <div class=\"description\">\r\n                        <img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s19/M00/1C/3F/CoNHgmIm7dEMo6HnAAB0qqKHbfE.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%2130x30r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%2130x30%2Fquality%2F90\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\">\r\n                        漫悠旅行\r\n                        <span class=\"lv\">Lv.35</span>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <p>江苏在我的印象里，似乎都和水乡相关。这次来到了兵家必争之地徐州&nbsp;，在三天的行走里，发现徐州&nbsp;不止是水乡，还是一座多元化的宝藏城市。<br>\r\n当你走过龟山汉墓、汉文化景区，戏马台时，你会深感这座城市两汉历史之悠久，文化之厚重；<br>\r\n当你走过户部山古民居、回龙窝、马庄时，你会惊叹于这座城市民间建筑之精美，民俗之精彩；<br>\r\n当你走过彭祖园、云龙山、云龙湖、潘安湖、潘安水镇时，你会流连于这座城市的山水之优美。</p>\r\n                </section>\r\n            </div>\r\n        \r\n\r\n                                        <div class=\"f-block\" id=\"_j_paragraph_2\"><h2>什么时候去徐州玩合适</h2></div>\r\n                    \r\n\r\n                                        <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                    <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/7A/A0/wKgBs1cTq1aAfSJ8AArNzmntiT013.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/7A/A0/wKgBs1cTq1aAfSJ8AArNzmntiT013.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/7A/A0/wKgBs1cTq1aAfSJ8AArNzmntiT013.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"display: block;\">\r\n                    <span class=\"img-an\">\r\n                                                     by 小小莎老师\r\n                                            </span>\r\n                </div>\r\n                            <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                    <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/82/8E/wKgBs1cTynKAKvLxAAwAKmaflQQ64.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/82/8E/wKgBs1cTynKAKvLxAAwAKmaflQQ64.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/82/8E/wKgBs1cTynKAKvLxAAwAKmaflQQ64.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"display: block;\">\r\n                    <span class=\"img-an\">\r\n                                                     by 小小莎老师\r\n                                            </span>\r\n                </div>\r\n                    \r\n\r\n                        <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                <div class=\"p-section\">\r\n                    每年的<b>春秋两季</b>去徐州玩耍最为适宜<b>。</b>春季，云龙湖沿岸桃红柳绿梨花白，云龙山西坡十里杏花，美不胜收；金秋整座城市都开满了银杏，浪漫异常。\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        \r\n\r\n                                        <div class=\"f-block\" id=\"_j_paragraph_3\"><h2>徐州玩几天比较合适？</h2></div>\r\n                    \r\n\r\n                        <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                <div class=\"p-section\">\r\n                    去徐州一般安排<b>2～3天</b>比较合适<b>。</b>如果你想更为深入地了解苏北文化，不妨顺道去一趟与徐州临近的<b>连云港</b>。作为苏北的两个代表性旅游城市，这两座城市可以安排在一起。<br>\r\n<br>\r\n在这两地，不仅能走老街旧巷，寻古探幽；还能看山水风景，旖旎风光。如果喜欢大海，还可以去连云港周边的海岛走走逛逛，吹吹海风。关于连云港的攻略，可查看👇\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        \r\n\r\n                        <div class=\"f-block raiders clearfix\">\r\n                <a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/gonglve/ziyouxing/405422.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"_j_quote_guide\" data-guidename=\"徐州出行须知！行前看这篇就够了\" data-quote-name=\"连云港行前必备！第一次去看这篇就够了\" data-id=\"405422\" data-type=\"1\">\r\n                    <div class=\"img\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s18/M00/25/77/CoUBYGDUvyOAArCcAAiaz8H4gYc92.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21231x160r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21231x160%2Fquality%2F100\"></div>\r\n                    <div class=\"info\">\r\n                        <h2>连云港行前必备！第一次去看这篇就够了</h2>\r\n                        <ul class=\"pro-list\">\r\n                                                                                                <li>初识港城</li>\r\n                                                                                                                                <li>最佳旅游时间</li>\r\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    </ul>\r\n                        <div class=\"count\"><i class=\"look\"></i>71289<i class=\"star\"></i>907</div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class=\"tips\"><span>攻略</span></div>\r\n                </a>\r\n            </div>\r\n        \r\n\r\n                                        <div class=\"f-block\" id=\"_j_paragraph_4\"><h2>徐州交通一览</h2></div>\r\n                    \r\n\r\n                        <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                <div class=\"p-section\">\r\n                    徐州是重要的交通枢纽城市，外部交通十分便捷，火车、飞机、客车样样通达；徐州内部交通便利，公交车、出租车很多，游客出行还是比较方便的。\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        \r\n\r\n                                        <div class=\"f-block\" id=\"_j_paragraph_5\"><h3>如何抵达徐州</h3></div>\r\n                    \r\n\r\n                        <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                <div class=\"p-section\">\r\n                    <b>【飞机】</b><br>\r\n徐州的<b>观音国际机场</b>拥有两座航站楼，距离徐州市区45公里，已开通与国内多个城市的航线，包括直飞香港等航班；国际航线目前已开通直达曼谷的航班。\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        \r\n\r\n                        <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                <section class=\"travelnote\">\r\n                    <div class=\"description\">\r\n                        <img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/9F/57/wKgED1vSdN6AATzuAAaioLF_aig87.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%2130x30r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%2130x30%2Fquality%2F90\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\">\r\n                        马蜂窝攻略组\r\n                        <span class=\"lv\">Lv.45</span>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <p>1.&nbsp;如到市区，可去机场候机楼一楼到达厅前乘坐机场大巴；如去机场，可以在徐州汽车总站⌈老火车站⌉、中汇国际酒店（矿业大学文昌校区）、徐州汽车东站乘坐机场大巴，票价25元。<br>\r\n2.&nbsp;此外，观音机场还有开往枣庄、新沂、邳州、宿迁等临近城市的机场巴士。如有疑问，可拨打服务热线&nbsp;：0516-83707677</p>\r\n                </section>\r\n            </div>\r\n        \r\n\r\n                        <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                <div class=\"p-section\">\r\n                    <b>【火车站】</b><br>\r\n<br>\r\n徐州是全国重要的综合性交通枢纽，“米”字形高铁枢纽已开通6个方向，单是高铁就通达全国25个省会城市。乘搭火车可到达徐州站、徐州东站、徐州西站、徐州北站、徐州南站等。\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        \r\n\r\n                                        <div class=\"f-block\" id=\"_j_paragraph_6\"><h3>徐州市区内如何出行</h3></div>\r\n                    \r\n\r\n                        <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                <div class=\"p-section\">\r\n                    在徐州，可以搭乘地铁（1号、2号、3号线）、公交等公共交通工具，也可以打车，出行很方便。\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        \r\n\r\n                                        <div class=\"f-block\" id=\"_j_paragraph_7\"><h2>去徐州住哪里</h2></div>\r\n                    \r\n\r\n                        <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"height: 478px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s18/M00/72/A9/CoUBYGBr4lyAfnffAAf_D6iqAGE606.JPG?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s18/M00/72/A9/CoUBYGBr4lyAfnffAAf_D6iqAGE606.JPG?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s18/M00/72/A9/CoUBYGBr4lyAfnffAAf_D6iqAGE606.JPG?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\">\r\n                <span class=\"img-an\">\r\n                                             by JOJO带你游世界\r\n                                    </span>\r\n            </div>\r\n        \r\n\r\n                        <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                <div class=\"p-section\">\r\n                    徐州景点相对比较集中，对于大部分游客来说，<b>住在市中心是最方便的选择。</b>价格由俭入奢，丰俭由人。\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        \r\n\r\n                                        <div class=\"f-block\" id=\"_j_paragraph_8\"><h3>苏宁广场亚朵酒店</h3></div>\r\n                    \r\n\r\n                        <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                <div class=\"p-section\">\r\n                    亚朵算是性价比较高的连锁酒店，整体环境自在舒心。酒店毗邻复兴苏宁广场、戏马台、回龙窝景区，距徐州汉文化景区、彭祖园约2公里，距云龙湖景区约4公里，另外紧邻地铁3号线，交通也十分方便。\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        \r\n\r\n                                        <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                    <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://hotel.mafengwo.net/mfs/s13/M00/A7/50/wKgEaVydin2Aa3jyAAEoYxhS79099.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://hotel.mafengwo.net/mfs/s13/M00/A7/50/wKgEaVydin2Aa3jyAAEoYxhS79099.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://hotel.mafengwo.net/mfs/s13/M00/A7/50/wKgEaVydin2Aa3jyAAEoYxhS79099.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"display: block;\">\r\n                    <span class=\"img-an\">\r\n                                                    \r\n                                            </span>\r\n                </div>\r\n                            <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                    <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://hotel.mafengwo.net/mfs/s13/M00/A8/8E/wKgEaVydiwKAFAdMAAHLGTuZUN872.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://hotel.mafengwo.net/mfs/s13/M00/A8/8E/wKgEaVydiwKAFAdMAAHLGTuZUN872.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://hotel.mafengwo.net/mfs/s13/M00/A8/8E/wKgEaVydiwKAFAdMAAHLGTuZUN872.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"display: block;\">\r\n                    <span class=\"img-an\">\r\n                                                    \r\n                                            </span>\r\n                </div>\r\n                    \r\n\r\n                        <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                <div class=\"p-section\">\r\n                    <b>地址：</b>建国东路219号<br>\r\n<b>参考价格：</b>300元起/晚\r\n\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        \r\n\r\n                        <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                                    <div class=\"pro_list\">\r\n                        <div class=\"tit\"></div>\r\n                        <div class=\"pro clearfix\">\r\n                            <a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/hotel/7380288.html\" target=\"_blank\">\r\n                                <div class=\"pic\"><img src=\"https://hotel.mafengwo.net/img/7c/78de8f093d08354411decafe2306ef9a.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21140x90r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21140x90%2Fquality%2F100\" alt=\"徐州建国东路苏宁广场亚朵酒店\" width=\"180\" height=\"100\"></div>\r\n                                <div class=\"info\">\r\n                                    <div class=\"info_title\">徐州建国东路苏宁广场亚朵酒店</div>\r\n                                    <div class=\"desc\">\r\n                                        \r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <div class=\"pro_det\">\r\n                                                                        <span class=\"price\">¥<b>340</b></span>\r\n                                                                            \r\n                                </div>\r\n                            </a>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n        \r\n\r\n                                        <div class=\"f-block\" id=\"_j_paragraph_9\"><h3>徐州苏宁凯悦</h3></div>\r\n                    \r\n\r\n                        <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                <div class=\"p-section\">\r\n                    坐落于徐州市中心地标建筑苏宁广场主楼，毗邻徐州苏宁购物中心，地理位置极佳。整体装修偏向于大气沉稳，可以俯瞰云龙湖全貌和城市胜景，整体偏向于豪华舒适。\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        \r\n\r\n                                        <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                    <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://hotel.mafengwo.net/mfs/s17/M00/48/B0/CoUBXl_qRj6AEVqcAAVcUpxtdQA43.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://hotel.mafengwo.net/mfs/s17/M00/48/B0/CoUBXl_qRj6AEVqcAAVcUpxtdQA43.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://hotel.mafengwo.net/mfs/s17/M00/48/B0/CoUBXl_qRj6AEVqcAAVcUpxtdQA43.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"display: block;\">\r\n                    <span class=\"img-an\">\r\n                                                    \r\n                                            </span>\r\n                </div>\r\n                            <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                    <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://hotel.mafengwo.net/mfs/s12/M00/66/73/wKgED1xAYJWAG6AXAAPbsdhX_Q847.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://hotel.mafengwo.net/mfs/s12/M00/66/73/wKgED1xAYJWAG6AXAAPbsdhX_Q847.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://hotel.mafengwo.net/mfs/s12/M00/66/73/wKgED1xAYJWAG6AXAAPbsdhX_Q847.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"display: block;\">\r\n                    <span class=\"img-an\">\r\n                                                    \r\n                                            </span>\r\n                </div>\r\n                            <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                    <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://hotel.mafengwo.net/mfs/s13/M00/BF/D1/wKgEaVyx9yCADzuoAAvc5rMq_WQ41.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://hotel.mafengwo.net/mfs/s13/M00/BF/D1/wKgEaVyx9yCADzuoAAvc5rMq_WQ41.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://hotel.mafengwo.net/mfs/s13/M00/BF/D1/wKgEaVyx9yCADzuoAAvc5rMq_WQ41.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"display: block;\">\r\n                    <span class=\"img-an\">\r\n                                                    \r\n                                            </span>\r\n                </div>\r\n                    \r\n\r\n                        <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                <div class=\"p-section\">\r\n                    <b>地址&nbsp;:&nbsp;</b>江苏省徐州市鼓楼区淮海东路29号<br>\r\n<b>参考价格：</b>600元起/晚\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        \r\n\r\n                        <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                                    <div class=\"pro_list\">\r\n                        <div class=\"tit\"></div>\r\n                        <div class=\"pro clearfix\">\r\n                            <a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/hotel/69800348.html\" target=\"_blank\">\r\n                                <div class=\"pic\"><img src=\"https://hotel.mafengwo.net/img/57/7bfe08d9c3e712794f02bb6c761f2ac1.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21140x90r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21140x90%2Fquality%2F100\" alt=\"徐州苏宁凯悦酒店\" width=\"180\" height=\"100\"></div>\r\n                                <div class=\"info\">\r\n                                    <div class=\"info_title\">徐州苏宁凯悦酒店</div>\r\n                                    <div class=\"desc\">\r\n                                        \r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <div class=\"pro_det\">\r\n                                                                        <span class=\"price\">¥<b>538</b></span>\r\n                                                                            \r\n                                </div>\r\n                            </a>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n        \r\n\r\n    \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n            </div>', 11110, '2024-07-08');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES (2, '成都精华景点丨老成都、夜生活、文艺范（附路线安排）', '来到成都，不论是网红地标IFS，春熙路步行街、远洋太古里等市区繁华商圈，还是武侯祠、宽窄巷子、杜甫草堂代表巴蜀文化的历史遗迹，亦或者周边的峨眉山、乐山、青城山的好风景，都非常值得游览。', 'http://localhost:8080/files/download/88.jpeg', '<div class=\"_j_content\">\r\n                                        <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                <div class=\"p-section\">\r\n                    来到成都，不论是<b>网红地标</b>IFS，春熙路步行街、远洋太古里等市区繁华商圈，还是武侯祠、宽窄巷子、杜甫草堂代表<b>巴蜀文化</b>的历史遗迹，亦或者周边的峨眉山、乐山、青城山的好风景，都非常值得游览。\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        \r\n\r\n                                        <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                    <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s17/M00/95/D5/CoUBXl-z6b6AREmsAAplbmJub-g535.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s17/M00/95/D5/CoUBXl-z6b6AREmsAAplbmJub-g535.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s17/M00/95/D5/CoUBXl-z6b6AREmsAAplbmJub-g535.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"display: block;\">\r\n                    <span class=\"img-an\">\r\n                                                    IFS by 秀山水旅行\r\n                                            </span>\r\n                </div>\r\n                            <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                    <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s17/M00/95/C7/CoUBXl-z6beAAqzQAAQFimZGc0w879.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s17/M00/95/C7/CoUBXl-z6beAAqzQAAQFimZGc0w879.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s17/M00/95/C7/CoUBXl-z6beAAqzQAAQFimZGc0w879.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"display: block;\">\r\n                    <span class=\"img-an\">\r\n                                                    宽窄巷子 by 秀山水旅行\r\n                                            </span>\r\n                </div>\r\n                            <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                    <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s17/M00/A9/C9/CoUBXl-ktIWAbGrcAAe1sGeaU6M10.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s17/M00/A9/C9/CoUBXl-ktIWAbGrcAAe1sGeaU6M10.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s17/M00/A9/C9/CoUBXl-ktIWAbGrcAAe1sGeaU6M10.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"display: block;\">\r\n                    <span class=\"img-an\">\r\n                                                    人民公园\r\n                                            </span>\r\n                </div>\r\n                            <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                    <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/38/D0/CoUBUl8LFxWAZ1EsACGt1yFRaDA613.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/38/D0/CoUBUl8LFxWAZ1EsACGt1yFRaDA613.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/38/D0/CoUBUl8LFxWAZ1EsACGt1yFRaDA613.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"display: block;\">\r\n                    <span class=\"img-an\">\r\n                                                    武侯祠 by 150少女\r\n                                            </span>\r\n                </div>\r\n                            <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                    <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/2F/50/CoUBUl60K5yACaWeAA0OMmLYA1o706.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/2F/50/CoUBUl60K5yACaWeAA0OMmLYA1o706.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/2F/50/CoUBUl60K5yACaWeAA0OMmLYA1o706.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"display: block;\">\r\n                    <span class=\"img-an\">\r\n                                                    九眼桥 by 150少女\r\n                                            </span>\r\n                </div>\r\n                            <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                    <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s14/M00/A0/63/wKgE2l1uY7yAcgdfAAOtSnC1tZc945.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s14/M00/A0/63/wKgE2l1uY7yAcgdfAAOtSnC1tZc945.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s14/M00/A0/63/wKgE2l1uY7yAcgdfAAOtSnC1tZc945.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"display: block;\">\r\n                    <span class=\"img-an\">\r\n                                                    杜甫草堂 by 150少女\r\n                                            </span>\r\n                </div>\r\n                    \r\n\r\n                        <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                <div class=\"p-section\">\r\n                    大多数第一次去成都的旅游者，会给成都市区3-5天的旅游时间，想要在有限的时间里，逛到自己喜欢的精华景点，仔细阅读本攻略，希望能给你的出行带来建议和决策。\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        \r\n\r\n                        <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"height: 462px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/07/db/8a6db3870b6b6b912edbef676f60f7e4.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/07/db/8a6db3870b6b6b912edbef676f60f7e4.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/07/db/8a6db3870b6b6b912edbef676f60f7e4.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\">\r\n                <span class=\"img-an\">\r\n                                            \r\n                                    </span>\r\n            </div>\r\n        \r\n\r\n                        <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                <div class=\"p-section\">\r\n                    到达这些景点集中在成都市区，都可以坐地铁到达，也可以坐出租车。\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        \r\n\r\n                        <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                <section class=\"travelnote\">\r\n                    <div class=\"description\">\r\n                        <img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/9F/57/wKgED1vSdN6AATzuAAaioLF_aig87.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%2130x30r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%2130x30%2Fquality%2F90\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\">\r\n                        马蜂窝攻略组\r\n                        <span class=\"lv\">Lv.45</span>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <p>成都金沙遗址也能看超火的“三星堆”<b>同款遗址文物啦</b>，快来看看！</p>\r\n                </section>\r\n            </div>\r\n        \r\n\r\n                                        <div class=\"f-block\" id=\"_j_paragraph_1\"><h2>一、玩转“老成都”</h2></div>\r\n                    \r\n\r\n                                        <div class=\"f-block\" id=\"_j_paragraph_2\"><h3>宽窄巷子</h3></div>\r\n                    \r\n\r\n                        <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                <div class=\"p-section\">\r\n                    <b>亮点：古建筑，文艺，体验传统活动</b><br>\r\n宽窄巷子是成都市区最具代表性的景点，包括宽巷子、窄巷子、井巷子三条平行的巷子。这里由当地古建筑改造而成，是老成都的生活缩影，曲折蜿蜒的小路两边布满特色商店和成都小吃，喝茶、掏耳朵、川剧变脸等活动应有尽有，能够很好地体验巴蜀的人文特色和民俗文化。\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        \r\n\r\n                        <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"height: 460px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s17/M00/EA/56/CoUBXl-7ifqAMmtoAAsHBRg8CRA776.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s17/M00/EA/56/CoUBXl-7ifqAMmtoAAsHBRg8CRA776.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s17/M00/EA/56/CoUBXl-7ifqAMmtoAAsHBRg8CRA776.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\">\r\n                <span class=\"img-an\">\r\n                                            图片来自网络\r\n                                    </span>\r\n            </div>\r\n        \r\n\r\n                        <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                <div class=\"p-section\">\r\n                    清晨<b>8:00-10:00，宽窄巷子人比较少，</b>商铺还没有全开门，是游玩、拍照的最佳时间。<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<b>景区导览</b><br>\r\n关注微信公众号【宽窄巷子最成都】，点击【耍宽窄—聆听宽窄】可以听到宽窄巷子的音频导览，了解宽窄巷子的历史；点击【耍宽窄—宽窄地图】可以查看宽窄巷子的官方导览图。\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        \r\n\r\n                        <div class=\"f-block\">\r\n                <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"height: 393px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/4C/CB/CoUBUl_z4YaAOEw8AAc_5_BALDo31.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/4C/CB/CoUBUl_z4YaAOEw8AAc_5_BALDo31.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/4C/CB/CoUBUl_z4YaAOEw8AAc_5_BALDo31.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\">\r\n                <span class=\"img-an\">\r\n                                            图片来自网络\r\n                                    </span>\r\n            </div>\r\n        \r\n\r\n      \r\n\r\n            </div>', 23334, '2024-07-08');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES (3, '希腊  |  科孚岛寻找德雷尔一家的夏日', '人们对 希腊 的印象似乎停留在了它的自然之美，而古 希腊 的文明则成了记忆中遥不可及的一个幻梦。在曾经充斥着哲学家思辨之音的 雅典 城，文学、民主、哲学、礼仪这十年来都越来越像此地永远在挖掘着的古迹，存在过，辉煌过，但也像那众神一样忽然离去。', 'http://localhost:8080/files/download/77.jpeg', '<div class=\"vc_article\">\r\n                    \r\n                                        \r\n                                            <div class=\"va_con _j_master_content\" data-cs-t=\"ginfo_kw_hotel\">\r\n    <div class=\"block-loading loading_backward\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"_j_content_box\">\r\n	        <div data-seq=\"1882996193\" data-index=\"1\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"t1\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\">前言</span></h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1882996194\">\r\n                                                                                                        人们对\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10168.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"希腊\" target=\"_blank\">希腊</a>\r\n                                                                                                            的印象似乎停留在了它的自然之美，而古\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10168.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"希腊\" target=\"_blank\">希腊</a>\r\n                                                                                                            的文明则成了记忆中遥不可及的一个幻梦。在曾经充斥着哲学家思辨之音的\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"雅典\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>\r\n                                                                                                            城，文学、民主、哲学、礼仪这十年来都越来越像此地永远在挖掘着的古迹，存在过，辉煌过，但也像那众神一样忽然离去。这座曾点燃人类文明之光的城市，如今有些破败，看上去疲态尽显。但是当我在朋友的指引下，深入地去了解经济危机后的\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"雅典\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>\r\n                                                                                                            在如何努力改变自己后，我对于一座城市的美丑定义开始慢慢改变。或许，在所有的先人那里，\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"雅典\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>\r\n                                                                                                            本就无关乎善恶与美丑，而只是一场关于自由与有趣的讨论。而自由与有趣，正让当下的\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"雅典\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>\r\n                                                                                                            城开始变得善\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/145939.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"和美\" target=\"_blank\">和美</a>\r\n                                                                                                            。<br>\r\n\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1882996195\">\r\n                                                                                                        在散布在\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/17211.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"爱琴海\" target=\"_blank\">爱琴海</a>\r\n                                                                                                            中的两千个岛屿之间，\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/61658.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"科孚岛\" target=\"_blank\">科孚岛</a>\r\n                                                                                                            隐藏在\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"雅典\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>\r\n                                                                                                            的\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/31808.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"西北\" target=\"_blank\">西北</a>\r\n                                                                                                            海面，地理位置的相对隔离，成了我在\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10168.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"希腊\" target=\"_blank\">希腊</a>\r\n                                                                                                            最具梦幻的一周。所有关于德雷尔一家的记忆，遍布山丘的古老橄榄树，原始民风的山间小镇，清晨傍晚的粉红海面，都会让人确信，德雷尔为何会在此说出：“在\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/61658.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"科孚岛\" target=\"_blank\">科孚岛</a>\r\n                                                                                                            ，你会感恩出生于这个世界。”。<br>\r\n\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898369634\" data-seq=\"1898369635\" data-pid=\"1898369634\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10168/scenery_24513881/1898369634.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 826px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/78/a2/b6ca1d3b549b292256677f8154541dd3.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/78/a2/b6ca1d3b549b292256677f8154541dd3.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/78/a2/b6ca1d3b549b292256677f8154541dd3.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898369634\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898369663\">\r\n                                                                            <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/61658.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"科孚岛\" target=\"_blank\">科孚岛</a>\r\n                                                                                                            的海上白色教堂\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1882996197\" data-seq=\"1882996198\" data-pid=\"1882996197\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10168/scenery_24513881/1882996197.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 421px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/4a/0f/5177a7882f832b9bb7bc2037761ba1de.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/4a/0f/5177a7882f832b9bb7bc2037761ba1de.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/4a/0f/5177a7882f832b9bb7bc2037761ba1de.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1882996197\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898369603\">\r\n                                                                                                        清晨的粉红\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/61658.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"科孚岛\" target=\"_blank\">科孚岛</a>\r\n                                                                                                            <br>\r\n\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898399132\" data-seq=\"1898399300\" data-pid=\"1898399132\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10168/scenery_24513881/1898399132.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1015px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/0b/7c/15d82ef03026bdb2d5f67509faf08320.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/0b/7c/15d82ef03026bdb2d5f67509faf08320.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/0b/7c/15d82ef03026bdb2d5f67509faf08320.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898399132\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898399317\">\r\n                                                                            <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/61658.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"科孚岛\" target=\"_blank\">科孚岛</a>\r\n                                                                                                            的果冻海\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n     \r\n\r\n                                    </div>', 22344, '2024-07-08');
