   <!-- <img src=\'h\' style=\'width:hpx;\' />-->\r\n                        <img src=\"https://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/124@2x.png\">\r\n                                                                                <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10068.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"哈尔滨\" target=\"_blank\">哈尔滨</a>\r\n                                                                                                            ，穿越乌带公路、桃南公路和207省道，机场还车，住\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10068.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"哈尔滨\" target=\"_blank\">哈尔滨</a>\r\n                                                                                                            机场酒店<br>\r\nDay10：9月28日，\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10068.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"哈尔滨\" target=\"_blank\">哈尔滨</a>\r\n                                                                                <!-- <img src=\'h\' style=\'width:hpx;\' />-->\r\n                        <img src=\"https://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/114@2x.png\">\r\n                                                                                <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10132.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"厦门\" target=\"_blank\">厦门</a>\r\n                                                                                                            。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div data-seq=\"1898852963\" data-index=\"4\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"t9\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\">【Day1】厦门飞哈尔滨</span></h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898852964\">\r\n                                                                                                        航班信息\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898853132\" data-seq=\"1898853133\" data-pid=\"1898853132\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11473/scenery_24516699/1898853132.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 211px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/5d/ef/b59523d5161db08e4de1e16de1db75c0.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/5d/ef/b59523d5161db08e4de1e16de1db75c0.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/5d/ef/b59523d5161db08e4de1e16de1db75c0.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898853132\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898853146\">\r\n                                                                                                        <br>\r\n取完行李租车后直接开往预订市区的中央大街附近酒店，由于\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/16215.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"东北\" target=\"_blank\">东北</a>\r\n                                                                                                            秋季天黑比较早，办理入住手续天基本上黑了，懒得出去逛街，就在附近找家餐厅吃晚饭和超市购物，回酒店休息。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div data-seq=\"1898854096\" data-index=\"5\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"t9\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\">【Day2】扎龙湿地：鹤舞九天的童话世界</span></h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898854102\">\r\n                                                                                                        9月20日上午8：00从\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10068.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"哈尔滨\" target=\"_blank\">哈尔滨</a>\r\n                                                                                                            出发，驱车约320公里穿越松嫩平原，中午到达\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11709.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"齐齐哈尔\" target=\"_blank\">齐齐哈尔</a>\r\n                                                                                                            扎龙湿地生态旅游区，入住景区宾馆后为了赶上下午15:30最后一场丹顶鹤放飞表演，我们在13:45就进入景区。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898854685\" data-seq=\"1898854725\" data-pid=\"1898854685\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11473/scenery_24516699/1898854685.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/48/f0/e3e81c7e5ca9f88d9b01c1eed5556e72.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/48/f0/e3e81c7e5ca9f88d9b01c1eed5556e72.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/48/f0/e3e81c7e5ca9f88d9b01c1eed5556e72.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898854685\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898854686\" data-seq=\"1898854726\" data-pid=\"1898854686\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11473/scenery_24516699/1898854686.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/d6/78/16014efef67653f360cc07dd5f128e03.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/d6/78/16014efef67653f360cc07dd5f128e03.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/d6/78/16014efef67653f360cc07dd5f128e03.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898854686\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898854687\" data-seq=\"1898854727\" data-pid=\"1898854687\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11473/scenery_24516699/1898854687.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/3c/aa/f2392f6bc0e53219f7b253c45b05d0b5.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/3c/aa/f2392f6bc0e53219f7b253c45b05d0b5.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/3c/aa/f2392f6bc0e53219f7b253c45b05d0b5.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898854687\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898854688\" data-seq=\"1898854728\" data-pid=\"1898854688\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11473/scenery_24516699/1898854688.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/1b/b8/4d5d3ad955795364e0e0b320f91974ed.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/1b/b8/4d5d3ad955795364e0e0b320f91974ed.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/1b/b8/4d5d3ad955795364e0e0b320f91974ed.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898854688\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898854689\" data-seq=\"1898854729\" data-pid=\"1898854689\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11473/scenery_24516699/1898854689.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/27/84/eefa14239d0a8b6a49cf8869e6edc16b.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/27/84/eefa14239d0a8b6a49cf8869e6edc16b.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/27/84/eefa14239d0a8b6a49cf8869e6edc16b.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898854689\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898854691\" data-seq=\"1898854731\" data-pid=\"1898854691\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11473/scenery_24516699/1898854691.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/b5/8c/9a4691763bdb60c29c757278c3808b3d.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/b5/8c/9a4691763bdb60c29c757278c3808b3d.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898854691\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898854862\">\r\n                                                                                                        扎龙湿地是一片神奇的土地，这里芦苇摇曳，水波荡漾，是无数珍稀鸟类的家园，更是被誉为“仙鹤故乡”的扎龙湿地。这里不仅是丹顶鹤的栖息地，更是每一个热爱自然的人心中的圣地。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898854692\" data-seq=\"1898854732\" data-pid=\"1898854692\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11473/scenery_24516699/1898854692.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/73/a4/00e9c3f05d11f95b0e570886146dd0b2.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/73/a4/00e9c3f05d11f95b0e570886146dd0b2.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898854692\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898854693\" data-seq=\"1898854733\" data-pid=\"1898854693\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11473/scenery_24516699/1898854693.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/a4/6b/bc987838b4e7898db0383a19b0e9cb43.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/a4/6b/bc987838b4e7898db0383a19b0e9cb43.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898854693\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898854993\">\r\n                                                                                                        踏入扎龙湿地，仿佛进入了一个神秘的自然王国。这里的湿地生态系统保持着原始的风貌，湖泊、沼泽、草甸交织成一幅幅动人的自然画卷。扎龙湿地不仅是\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"中国\" target=\"_blank\">中国</a>\r\n                                                                                                            最大的\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/26088.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"淡水\" target=\"_blank\">淡水</a>\r\n                                                                                                            芦苇沼泽湿地，更是世界重要的湿地保护地之一。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898854694\" data-seq=\"1898854734\" data-pid=\"1898854694\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11473/scenery_24516699/1898854694.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/bd/f5/2d700d10d7cdf804c5267975f865d8e1.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/bd/f5/2d700d10d7cdf804c5267975f865d8e1.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898854694\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898854695\" data-seq=\"1898854735\" data-pid=\"1898854695\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11473/scenery_24516699/1898854695.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/45/64/1615fe1cfe18a647bac01a574b900037.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/45/64/1615fe1cfe18a647bac01a574b900037.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898854695\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898854696\" data-seq=\"1898854736\" data-pid=\"1898854696\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11473/scenery_24516699/1898854696.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/b3/76/0ca16a33b355bcc1b597eaa29512bd9b.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/b3/76/0ca16a33b355bcc1b597eaa29512bd9b.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898854696\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898854697\" data-seq=\"1898854737\" data-pid=\"1898854697\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11473/scenery_24516699/1898854697.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/6c/ff/885bea448b95ae5cb60953f0c705892c.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/6c/ff/885bea448b95ae5cb60953f0c705892c.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898854697\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898854959\">\r\n                                                                                                        丹顶鹤，湿地的精灵。在这片广袤的湿地中，最引人注目的莫过于那些优雅的丹顶鹤。它们或在芦苇丛中漫步，或在蓝天白云下展翅飞翔，每一次起飞都如同一场视觉的盛宴，全世界仅存丹顶鹤不足2000只，而扎龙湿地就有400多只。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n    \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-loading loading_forward\"></div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n    <div class=\"vc_total _j_help_total\">\r\n        本篇游记共含<span>13351</span>个文字，<span>459</span>张图片。帮助了<b class=\"_j_total_person\" style=\"font-weight:inherit\">622</b>名<b class=\"_j_total_mdd\" style=\"font-weight:inherit\">伊春</b>游客。\r\n        <a class=\"r-report\" data-japp=\"report\" data-refer-uid=\"10886962\" data-busi-id=\"id:24516699\" data-refer=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/i/24516699.html\" data-app=\"youji\">举报</a>    </div>\r\n\r\n                                    </div>', 1, '2024-09-03 11:00', 678, '2024-07-19', '7000', '10', '伊春', '通过');
INSERT INTO `travels` VALUES (5, '一场演唱会衍生的南洋狂想：狮城快闪 • 大马慢摇', 'http://localhost:8080/files/download/55.jpeg', '一切源于一场演唱会\r\n2023年6月，泰勒·斯威夫特官宣了她的 亚洲 演唱会行程。\r\n可惜的是， 亚洲 场次仅有 日本 和 新加坡 两站。\r\n作为一名追随了她十多年的忠实粉丝，我心中燃起了希望，决定无论如何都要抢到一张票。\r\n我尝试同时抢 日本 和 新加坡 的门票，这期间历经波折与失望，还好最终幸运地获得了 新加坡 3月3日演唱会的门票。', '<div class=\"vc_article\">\r\n                    \r\n                                        \r\n                                            <div class=\"va_con _j_master_content\" data-cs-t=\"ginfo_kw_hotel\">\r\n    <div class=\"block-loading loading_backward\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"_j_content_box\">\r\n	        <div data-seq=\"1898439278\" data-index=\"1\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"t9\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\">一切源于一场演唱会</span></h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898439296\">\r\n                                                                                                        2023年6月，泰勒·斯威夫特官宣了她的\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/52314.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"亚洲\" target=\"_blank\">亚洲</a>\r\n                                                                                                            演唱会行程。<br>\r\n可惜的是，\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/52314.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"亚洲\" target=\"_blank\">亚洲</a>\r\n                                                                                                            场次仅有\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10183.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"日本\" target=\"_blank\">日本</a>\r\n                                                                                                            和\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10754.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"新加坡\" target=\"_blank\">新加坡</a>\r\n                                                                                                            两站。<br>\r\n作为一名追随了她十多年的忠实粉丝，我心中燃起了希望，决定无论如何都要抢到一张票。<br>\r\n我尝试同时抢\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10183.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"日本\" target=\"_blank\">日本</a>\r\n                                                                                                            和\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10754.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"新加坡\" target=\"_blank\">新加坡</a>\r\n                                                                                                            的门票，这期间历经波折与失望，还好最终幸运地获得了\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10754.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"新加坡\" target=\"_blank\">新加坡</a>\r\n                                                                                                            3月3日演唱会的门票。<br>\r\n有了这张珍贵的门票，我开始马不停蹄地规划行程。<br>\r\n今年各个国家的政策也相当友好，\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10754.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"新加坡\" target=\"_blank\">新加坡</a>\r\n                                                                                                            和\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10097.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"马来西亚\" target=\"_blank\">马来西亚</a>\r\n                                                                                                            先后对\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"中国\" target=\"_blank\">中国</a>\r\n                                                                                                            实行免签政策，这让我可以无拘无束地在这两个国家之间穿梭游玩。于是，我决定把\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10754.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"新加坡\" target=\"_blank\">新加坡</a>\r\n                                                                                                            和\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10097.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"马来西亚\" target=\"_blank\">马来西亚</a>\r\n                                                                                                            的旅行结合起来，开启一段丰富多彩的双城之旅。<br>\r\n为了这碟醋包了一顿饺子，不过也有很多预料之外的快乐：\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898457592\">\r\n                                                                                                        💗被伊斯兰的艺术魅力深深吸引了;\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898457922\" data-seq=\"1898457923\" data-pid=\"1898457922\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\" data-poiid=\"5578271\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10097/scenery_24514198/1898457922.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1020px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/ce/7d/baeadeeec490d9d73c2419c5bced7eee.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/ce/7d/baeadeeec490d9d73c2419c5bced7eee.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/ce/7d/baeadeeec490d9d73c2419c5bced7eee.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898457922\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                                        <span class=\"pic_tag\">\r\n                <a href=\"/poi/5578271.html\" class=\"_j_anchor\" data-poiid=\"5578271\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">\r\n                    <i class=\"house\"></i>马来西亚伊斯兰艺术博物馆\r\n                </a>\r\n            </span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898327663\" data-seq=\"1898327763\" data-pid=\"1898327663\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\" data-poiid=\"5578271\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10097/scenery_24514198/1898327663.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/13/65/46972b87110c077b6e95b384b8791630.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/13/65/46972b87110c077b6e95b384b8791630.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/13/65/46972b87110c077b6e95b384b8791630.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898327663\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                                        <span class=\"pic_tag\">\r\n                <a href=\"/poi/5578271.html\" class=\"_j_anchor\" data-poiid=\"5578271\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">\r\n                    <i class=\"house\"></i>马来西亚伊斯兰艺术博物馆\r\n                </a>\r\n            </span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898456759\">\r\n                                                                                                        💗在喜欢的热带雨林中漫游，偶遇各种小动物；\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898440485\" data-seq=\"1898440486\" data-pid=\"1898440485\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10097/scenery_24514198/1898440485.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 906px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/a0/e3/0e02f8d0445d475854a2e247cc35f4f4.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/a0/e3/0e02f8d0445d475854a2e247cc35f4f4.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/a0/e3/0e02f8d0445d475854a2e247cc35f4f4.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898440485\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898457201\" data-seq=\"1898457202\" data-pid=\"1898457201\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\" data-poiid=\"5432079\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10097/scenery_24514198/1898457201.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1020px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/05/b3/79cda35e4aa03afac863f4f90d4667db.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/05/b3/79cda35e4aa03afac863f4f90d4667db.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/05/b3/79cda35e4aa03afac863f4f90d4667db.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898457201\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                                        <span class=\"pic_tag\">\r\n                <a href=\"/poi/5432079.html\" class=\"_j_anchor\" data-poiid=\"5432079\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">\r\n                    <i class=\"house\"></i>槟城升旗山\r\n                </a>\r\n            </span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898444339\" data-seq=\"1898444340\" data-pid=\"1898444339\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10097/scenery_24514198/1898444339.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 906px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/eb/fb/48cef6f18c3088148878b1ded42f19c1.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/eb/fb/48cef6f18c3088148878b1ded42f19c1.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/eb/fb/48cef6f18c3088148878b1ded42f19c1.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898444339\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898457244\">\r\n                                                                                                        💗不会游泳的我体验了被热带鱼群包围的快乐；\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898457259\" data-seq=\"1898457260\" data-pid=\"1898457259\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\" data-poiid=\"76089784\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10097/scenery_24514198/1898457259.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 379px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/87/00/8cd665f3a3a4a2707c826cf1e3c2bf31.png?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/87/00/8cd665f3a3a4a2707c826cf1e3c2bf31.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/87/00/8cd665f3a3a4a2707c826cf1e3c2bf31.png?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898457259\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                                        <span class=\"pic_tag\">\r\n                <a href=\"/poi/76089784.html\" class=\"_j_anchor\" data-poiid=\"76089784\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">\r\n                    <i class=\"house\"></i>马努干岛海底漫步\r\n                </a>\r\n            </span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                                <div class=\"video_wrapper _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898460066\">\r\n            <div class=\"add_video _j_seqitem \" data-vid=\"3567201\" data-seq=\"1898460066\" data-url=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/rest/app/note/video/3567201?jsondata=%7B%22data_style%22%3A%22jump%22%7D&amp;type=.m3u8\" data-type=\"2\" data-ready=\"1\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"800\" data-audit=\"0\"><video data-type=\"2\" width=\"680\" height=\"auto\" data-url=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/rest/app/note/video/3567201?jsondata=%7B%22data_style%22%3A%22jump%22%7D\" class=\"_js_videojs_hls\" data-noneedinit=\"0\" controls=\"\" src=\"blob:https://www.mafengwo.cn/f737fdbc-8da8-4f8a-aeac-c305a05faf21\"></video></div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n        \r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898445183\" data-seq=\"1898445184\" data-pid=\"1898445183\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10097/scenery_24514198/1898445183.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 382px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/e4/c3/e4cc32af45df720507fd59d2e4000779.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/e4/c3/e4cc32af45df720507fd59d2e4000779.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/e4/c3/e4cc32af45df720507fd59d2e4000779.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898445183\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898457963\">\r\n                                                                                                        💗日落，永远是大自然最动人的景色。无论它轮回多少次，就是无法厌倦；\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898458671\" data-seq=\"1898458672\" data-pid=\"1898458671\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\" data-poiid=\"5485715\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10097/scenery_24514198/1898458671.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1020px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/5d/7c/1470c7d9280cc720538abd9dbebabadb.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/5d/7c/1470c7d9280cc720538abd9dbebabadb.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/5d/7c/1470c7d9280cc720538abd9dbebabadb.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898458671\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                                        <span class=\"pic_tag\">\r\n                <a href=\"/poi/5485715.html\" class=\"_j_anchor\" data-poiid=\"5485715\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">\r\n                    <i class=\"house\"></i>丹绒亚路海滩\r\n                </a>\r\n            </span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898444400\" data-seq=\"1898444401\" data-pid=\"1898444400\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10097/scenery_24514198/1898444400.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 906px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/44/dc/18c82eeeb0988ce6609db66b8df2cadf.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/44/dc/18c82eeeb0988ce6609db66b8df2cadf.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/44/dc/18c82eeeb0988ce6609db66b8df2cadf.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898444400\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898444508\" data-seq=\"1898444509\" data-pid=\"1898444508\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10097/scenery_24514198/1898444508.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 509px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/ba/7f/9f46e73e982bf8c6f38da6f6642aca05.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/ba/7f/9f46e73e982bf8c6f38da6f6642aca05.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/ba/7f/9f46e73e982bf8c6f38da6f6642aca05.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898444508\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898440373\" data-seq=\"1898440374\" data-pid=\"1898440373\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10097/scenery_24514198/1898440373.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 906px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/da/7f/61b77259cc83f9ddb64235098a8b2c92.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/da/7f/61b77259cc83f9ddb64235098a8b2c92.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/da/7f/61b77259cc83f9ddb64235098a8b2c92.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898440373\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div data-seq=\"1898458126\" data-index=\"2\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"t9\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\">行程概览</span></h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898458131\">\r\n                                                                                                        因为Taylor Swift演唱会那几天\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10754.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"新加坡\" target=\"_blank\">新加坡</a>\r\n                                                                                                            的酒店价格很高，所以尽量缩减了在\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10754.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"新加坡\" target=\"_blank\">新加坡</a>\r\n                                                                                                            的时间。<br>\r\n个人认为\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10754.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"新加坡\" target=\"_blank\">新加坡</a>\r\n                                                                                                            和\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10097.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"马来西亚\" target=\"_blank\">马来西亚</a>\r\n                                                                                                            非常适合第一次出国的朋友们，如果你跟我一样喜欢自然和艺术，完全可以一比一复制我的行程。当然\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10754.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"新加坡\" target=\"_blank\">新加坡</a>\r\n                                                                                                            的行程还是有点\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/144799.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"太特\" target=\"_blank\">太特</a>\r\n                                                                                                            种兵了，分成两天玩会舒适很多。<br>\r\n✨每个景点后面我都会标注参观攻略，以及每个国家后面都有关于我踩过的坑的一些注意事项，大家可以在目录上随意跳转只取所需~\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898458472\" data-seq=\"1898458473\" data-pid=\"1898458472\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10097/scenery_24514198/1898458472.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 752px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/5c/1f/650c626e2097f2472a6e1e41e547a50e.png?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/5c/1f/650c626e2097f2472a6e1e41e547a50e.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/5c/1f/650c626e2097f2472a6e1e41e547a50e.png?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898458472\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div data-seq=\"1898458538\" data-index=\"3\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"t9\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\">---------新加坡篇---------</span></h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div data-seq=\"1898458555\" data-index=\"4\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"t9\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\">初见</span></h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898458572\">\r\n                                                                                                        第一次尝试一个人出国。<br>\r\n\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10754.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"新加坡\" target=\"_blank\">新加坡</a>\r\n                                                                                                            ，对于从小就生活在\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/16107.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"大城\" target=\"_blank\">大城</a>\r\n                                                                                                            市的我来说，并没有太大的诱惑力。<br>\r\n旁人一提起\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10754.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"新加坡\" target=\"_blank\">新加坡</a>\r\n                                                                                                            ，我的脑海里就会出现这样的画面：在一个会喷水的\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/145844.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"狮子\" target=\"_blank\">狮子</a>\r\n                                                                                                            雕塑旁，周围是高楼大厦，那是钢筋水泥组成的怪兽，无处不在地向游客展示高科技以及井井有条的生活方式。即使是公园，也是人工打造的精品，看那些勉强在铁丝巨网中生长的植物，对，我指的是它的地标性景点空中花园。还有过高的吃住成本，在理性驱动下实在没有太多放开去玩的冲动。<br>\r\n也许就是被这些先入为主的观念束缚着，我迟迟没定下行程路线，或许我应该随心所欲一点，看能否在其中碰撞出有趣火花。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898516969\" data-seq=\"1898516970\" data-pid=\"1898516969\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10097/scenery_24514198/1898516969.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 906px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/e7/e6/92bb74da3a92764b13136d10d2e3baf8.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/e7/e6/92bb74da3a92764b13136d10d2e3baf8.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/e7/e6/92bb74da3a92764b13136d10d2e3baf8.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898516969\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898516971\">\r\n                                                                                                        凌晨4点多到达\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10754.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"新加坡\" target=\"_blank\">新加坡</a>\r\n                                                                                                            樟宜机场，我想说\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10754.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"新加坡\" target=\"_blank\">新加坡</a>\r\n                                                                                                            会惩罚每一个不认真做攻略的人。<br>\r\n我原本想着到\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10754.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"新加坡\" target=\"_blank\">新加坡</a>\r\n                                                                                                            后先美滋滋地找个位置躺一觉，醒来之后逛逛\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64188.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"大名\" target=\"_blank\">大名</a>\r\n                                                                                                            鼎鼎的机场瀑布（那时候并不知道机场瀑布不是24小时开放的），差不多再去酒店办理入住。<br>\r\n然而我一下飞机，急速通过机器过关，去拿行李，打算找分布在机场各处的舒服躺椅，结果发现我兜兜转转了好久都找不到，再往前走一点点商铺又关门了一片漆黑。此时我已经拿行李出了到达大厅，并不能再回去找付费休息室，只好放弃折腾，随便找了个位置坐着休息。<br>\r\n既然机场逛不了，那我问一下能不能提前入住吧。结果发现自己没开国际漫游，又折腾了好久，最后操着一口不怎么流利的英语（谁懂应试教育下哑巴英语的痛）问到了如果想提前入住要加钱升级房型。<br>\r\n与其在机场浪费时间，那不如直接去酒店放下行李直接去逛吧。<br>\r\n<br>\r\n原本以为今天自己的遭遇已经够Drama了，不过，更Drama的永远在下一刻。<br>\r\n<br>\r\n看着在Grab上面叫的出租车在机场外绕了10几分钟，积压的怨气让我变得渐渐不耐烦，干脆不看手机了，反正还有一段距离。这个时候打车的人并不多，他们陆陆续续都上车了，除了我旁边的一位男生。这个时候来了一辆绿色小车，看着像是我叫的那辆，正准备拿行李，这时候旁边的男生径直的走到车那放行李并上车了，心想：好吧，难道我看错了？<br>\r\n疑惑地拿出手机走出门准备对车牌号，只见那男生又下车，一句句sorry地把行李从车里拿下来。<br>\r\n我面无表情看这在我面前发生的一切，呼，我终于可以上车了。<br>\r\n跟司机简单对话了几句英语后，他直接跟我说中文。惊讶的我，顺带把此前积累的所有消极情绪清空了，在跟他唠嗑的过程中倍感亲切。<br>\r\n他说在\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10754.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"新加坡\" target=\"_blank\">新加坡</a>\r\n                                                                                                            新生代会讲中文的华人已经很少了，他是家里人要求他学习中文，所以他才讲得那么好。不过，我后来未能遇见更多当地年轻人进行交谈，这个结论无法得到充分论证。但确实，我在入住酒店、问路、就餐等情况下，只要遇到年纪稍大的华人面孔，他们都能用中文交流。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div data-seq=\"1898517628\" data-index=\"5\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"t9\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\">独自一人在新加坡特种兵citywalk</span></h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898517811\">\r\n                                                                                                        顺利办理入住后，把行李寄存在酒店，开始citywalk。<br>\r\n<br>\r\n【打破对一座国家的偏见最好的方式就是身临其境。】<br>\r\n<br>\r\n本来打算随便逛逛的我，在对\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10754.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"新加坡\" target=\"_blank\">新加坡</a>\r\n                                                                                                            这座城市逐渐深入了解后，我贪婪地在有限的时间线上不断塞进一个个想去的地点。<br>\r\n<br>\r\n从我酒店所在的区域说起吧。<br>\r\n不得不说，Taylor Swift经济效应不是说笑的。想起之前看过一张梗图，画面上画着\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10062.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"美国\" target=\"_blank\">美国</a>\r\n                                                                                                            经济的两大支柱是英伟达和Taylor Swift。<br>\r\n在3月的巡回演出期间，附近的所有酒店几乎都涨价了一倍。我大概提前四个月订酒店，以为在半年前只是刚买完演唱会门票的人把酒店的价格推高而已，这时候价格应该会降一点。然而，好一点的酒店已经被订满了，剩下的选择不多。我这家感觉性价比不错，但也要1300多一晚，房间很小，15平左右，而且位置离演唱会场馆有将近5公里。<br>\r\n不过好处在于，它离\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/27870.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"东海\" target=\"_blank\">东海</a>\r\n                                                                                                            岸非常近近，也就是离大海很近，步行到\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/27870.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"东海\" target=\"_blank\">东海</a>\r\n                                                                                                            岸公园只需要13分钟。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898440798\" data-seq=\"1898440799\" data-pid=\"1898440798\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10097/scenery_24514198/1898440798.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 907px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/5d/ec/62c31d69c353530704c1d12c2b10c768.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/5d/ec/62c31d69c353530704c1d12c2b10c768.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/5d/ec/62c31d69c353530704c1d12c2b10c768.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898440798\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898440796\" data-seq=\"1898440797\" data-pid=\"1898440796\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10097/scenery_24514198/1898440796.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 906px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/7b/b6/61626eafc9ad51418477a89316a65ddb.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/7b/b6/61626eafc9ad51418477a89316a65ddb.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/7b/b6/61626eafc9ad51418477a89316a65ddb.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898440796\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898517955\">\r\n                                                                                                        这一带大部分都是住宅或者餐厅，以别墅为主，高楼大厦在这里反而显得突兀。<br>\r\n清晨七时半，天刚破晓，厚重的云层笼罩天空，挡住了阳光的光辉。走了一会，却见太阳在远方徐徐升起，橙色的光芒穿透云层，在墙上投下斑斓的印记。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n\r\n                                    </div>', 1, '2024-09-04 11:00', 700, '2024-07-19', '7000', '8', '马来西亚', '通过');
INSERT INTO `travels` VALUES (7, '树是梧桐树，城是南京城', 'http://localhost:8080/files/download/66.jpeg', '亲爱的旅客朋友，前方到站， 南京。火车夕发朝至，转乘地铁和小懒碰面，吃了 南京 的第一顿饭——鸭血粉丝汤，味道很棒  ，然后直奔景点啦。', '<div class=\"vc_article\">\r\n                    \r\n                                        \r\n                                            <div class=\"va_con _j_master_content\" data-cs-t=\"ginfo_kw_hotel\">\r\n    <div class=\"block-loading loading_backward\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"_j_content_box\">\r\n	        <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1896772537\">\r\n                                                                                                        亲爱的旅客朋友，前方到站，\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10684.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"南京\" target=\"_blank\">南京</a>\r\n                                                                                                            。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n															\r\n                       \r\n                    </div>\r\n        \r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1896772580\">\r\n                                                                                                        火车夕发朝至，转乘地铁和小懒碰面，吃了\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10684.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"南京\" target=\"_blank\">南京</a>\r\n                                                                                                            的第一顿饭——鸭血粉丝汤，味道很棒\r\n                                                                                                        <!-- <img src=\'h\' style=\'width:hpx;\' />-->\r\n                        <img src=\"https://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/29@2x.png\">\r\n                                                                                                            ，然后直奔景点啦。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1896772578\" data-seq=\"1896772579\" data-pid=\"1896772578\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1896772578.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 509px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/17/77/47bfdbc59d27fc452283729aa4f7ff3e.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/17/77/47bfdbc59d27fc452283729aa4f7ff3e.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/17/77/47bfdbc59d27fc452283729aa4f7ff3e.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1896772578\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div data-seq=\"1896772661\" data-index=\"1\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"t1\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\">Day1   钟山风景区</span></h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1896772658\">\r\n                                                                            <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10514.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"中山\" target=\"_blank\">中山</a>\r\n                                                                                                            陵<br>\r\n是\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"中国\" target=\"_blank\">中国</a>\r\n                                                                                                            近代建筑史上的第一陵，位于钟山中茅峰南麓，依山而筑，是伟大的民主革命先行者孙\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10514.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"中山\" target=\"_blank\">中山</a>\r\n                                                                                                            先生的陵墓。<br>\r\n牌坊→墓道→陵门→碑亭→祭堂→墓室在一条中轴线上——\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"中国\" target=\"_blank\">中国</a>\r\n                                                                                                            传统建筑风格，平行距离有七百米，高低落差七十米。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1896772814\" data-seq=\"1896772815\" data-pid=\"1896772814\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1896772814.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/da/ac/3d6d51086b75e8c2e84bbe97c91aa585.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/da/ac/3d6d51086b75e8c2e84bbe97c91aa585.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/da/ac/3d6d51086b75e8c2e84bbe97c91aa585.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1896772814\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1896772753\" data-seq=\"1896772754\" data-pid=\"1896772753\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1896772753.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/63/c7/ba74094e2797b6906d77e57851b5a466.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/63/c7/ba74094e2797b6906d77e57851b5a466.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/63/c7/ba74094e2797b6906d77e57851b5a466.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1896772753\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1896772762\" data-seq=\"1896772763\" data-pid=\"1896772762\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1896772762.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/3d/7c/67f67ed14952ca37d7ce08614df76a8e.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/3d/7c/67f67ed14952ca37d7ce08614df76a8e.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/3d/7c/67f67ed14952ca37d7ce08614df76a8e.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1896772762\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1896772759\" data-seq=\"1896772760\" data-pid=\"1896772759\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1896772759.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/34/1f/6689b8d8fcf3c166b1d3c633b4a590bb.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/34/1f/6689b8d8fcf3c166b1d3c633b4a590bb.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/34/1f/6689b8d8fcf3c166b1d3c633b4a590bb.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1896772759\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1896772764\" data-seq=\"1896772770\" data-pid=\"1896772764\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1896772764.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 680px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/43/83/38feafe0bf51f974489a45a8e9d83fae.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/43/83/38feafe0bf51f974489a45a8e9d83fae.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/43/83/38feafe0bf51f974489a45a8e9d83fae.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1896772764\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1896772755\" data-seq=\"1896772758\" data-pid=\"1896772755\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1896772755.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/eb/3a/f8b83a7c002dc4bc576736a98030b379.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/eb/3a/f8b83a7c002dc4bc576736a98030b379.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/eb/3a/f8b83a7c002dc4bc576736a98030b379.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1896772755\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1896773001\">\r\n                                                                                                        音乐台<br>\r\n位于\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10514.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"中山\" target=\"_blank\">中山</a>\r\n                                                                                                            陵博爱广场东南方，建于1932年至1933年。<br>\r\n音乐台平面为半圆形，圆心处建造舞台。台前边缘有三层波纹形层梯。台下紧围前沿，一汪月牙形睡莲池，池底有伏泉，池前依坡就势，修整成以50米为半径的半圆形盆状大草坪，放射形直道与半圆形圈道使之分割成12块小扇形草坪。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n                                <div class=\"video_wrapper _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897710192\">\r\n            <div class=\"add_video _j_seqitem \" data-vid=\"3563395\" data-seq=\"1897710192\" data-url=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/rest/app/note/video/3563395?jsondata=%7B%22data_style%22%3A%22jump%22%7D&amp;type=.m3u8\" data-type=\"2\" data-ready=\"1\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-audit=\"0\"><video data-type=\"2\" width=\"680\" height=\"auto\" data-url=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/rest/app/note/video/3563395?jsondata=%7B%22data_style%22%3A%22jump%22%7D\" class=\"_js_videojs_hls\" data-noneedinit=\"0\" controls=\"\" src=\"blob:https://www.mafengwo.cn/b6260902-a86b-4e8e-808d-419be37778bf\"></video></div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n        \r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1896773097\">\r\n                                                                                                        　抓拍两个小姐妹花，太可爱了吧\r\n                                                                                                        <!-- <img src=\'h\' style=\'width:hpx;\' />-->\r\n                        <img src=\"https://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/20@2x.png\">\r\n                                                        </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897776536\" data-seq=\"1897776537\" data-pid=\"1897776536\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1897776536.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 906px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/8f/bc/b8347b422ce031a5f60e5e4a18d3583d.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/8f/bc/b8347b422ce031a5f60e5e4a18d3583d.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/8f/bc/b8347b422ce031a5f60e5e4a18d3583d.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897776536\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897706755\">\r\n                                                                                                        美龄宫<br>\r\n“远东第一别墅”，国民政府主席官邸遗址，始建于1931年，1946年国民政府还都\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10684.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"南京\" target=\"_blank\">南京</a>\r\n                                                                                                            后，蒋介石与宋美龄常在此下榻、休息，故被称为“美龄宫”，蒋介石曾多次在此接待外宾。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897713664\" data-seq=\"1897713665\" data-pid=\"1897713664\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1897713664.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/e7/77/c5b5c3405e989db6e84dfced906270c4.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/e7/77/c5b5c3405e989db6e84dfced906270c4.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/e7/77/c5b5c3405e989db6e84dfced906270c4.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897713664\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div data-seq=\"1897864302\" data-index=\"2\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"t1\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\">一句梧桐美，种满南京城</span></h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897713960\">\r\n                                                                                                        俯瞰“美龄宫”（图片来自于景区的宣传图）\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10171.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"法国\" target=\"_blank\">法国</a>\r\n                                                                                                            梧桐包裹着吊坠项链般的别墅，满满爱意倾洒而出。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897713697\" data-seq=\"1897713698\" data-pid=\"1897713697\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1897713697.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/a8/53/ea26e81f2e09af6586505eebaa8d7797.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/a8/53/ea26e81f2e09af6586505eebaa8d7797.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/a8/53/ea26e81f2e09af6586505eebaa8d7797.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897713697\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897714007\">\r\n                                                                                                        主体建筑是一座三层重檐山式宫殿式建筑，外形为明清官式做法，顶覆绿色琉璃瓦，房檐的琉璃瓦雕着1000多只凤凰，在\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"中国\" target=\"_blank\">中国</a>\r\n                                                                                                            独一无二。<br>\r\n“西洋骨，\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"中国\" target=\"_blank\">中国</a>\r\n                                                                                                            皮”——钢筋混凝土结构，大面积的落地钢窗，中西合璧。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897713668\" data-seq=\"1897713669\" data-pid=\"1897713668\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width