c=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/4d/33/c577239a868cbee053e49ff688544d3c.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/4d/33/c577239a868cbee053e49ff688544d3c.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/4d/33/c577239a868cbee053e49ff688544d3c.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897962378\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897965178\">\r\n                                                                                                        6幅油画，展示了晚清和近代的历史<br>\r\n《厘治两江》<br>\r\n从左到右依次为张之洞、李鸿章、左宗棠、曾国藩、刘坤一\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897962370\" data-seq=\"1897962371\" data-pid=\"1897962370\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1897962370.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/13/5d/b2d798e523c3db110dd9bbb1de4ee992.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/13/5d/b2d798e523c3db110dd9bbb1de4ee992.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/13/5d/b2d798e523c3db110dd9bbb1de4ee992.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897962370\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897965331\">\r\n                                                                                                        《天国风云》<br>\r\n太平时期的重要人物<br>\r\n从左到右依次为杨秀清、洪秀全、洪宣