lt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897977065\">\r\n                                                                                                        去往鸡鸣寺的路上，路过了\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/66290.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"和平\" target=\"_blank\">和平</a>\r\n                                                                                                            公园，邂逅了钟楼（也称励士钟塔）。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897976660\" data-seq=\"1897977012\" data-pid=\"1897976660\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1897976660.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 905px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/65/32/09bff0ece3843c092ae935377e9ef7ba.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/65/32/09bff0ece3843c092ae935377e9ef7ba.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/65/32/09bff0ece3843c092ae935377e9ef7ba.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897976660\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897963100\">\r\n                                                                                                        <br>\r\n\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div data-seq=\"1898428875\" data-index=\"5\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"t1\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\">南朝第一寺</span></h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898428876\">\r\n                                                                                                        <br>\r\n古鸡鸣寺<br>\r\n始建于西晋\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/16334.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"永康\" target=\"_blank\">永康</a>\r\n                                                                                                            元年（300年），已有一千七百多年的历史，是\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10684.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"南京\" target=\"_blank\">南京</a>\r\n                                                                                                            最古老的梵刹和皇家寺庙之一，香火一直旺盛不衰，自古有“南朝第一寺”，“南朝四百八十寺”之首的美誉，南朝时期与\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64381.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"栖霞\" target=\"_blank\">栖霞</a>\r\n                                                                                                            寺、定山寺齐名，是南朝时期\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"中国\" target=\"_blank\">中国</a>\r\n                                                                                                            的佛教中心。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n                                <div class=\"video_wrapper _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897867757\">\r\n            <div class=\"add_video _j_seqitem \" data-vid=\"3563984\" data-seq=\"1897867757\" data-url=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/rest/app/note/video/3563984?jsondata=%7B%22data_style%22%3A%22jump%22%7D&amp;type=.m3u8\" data-type=\"2\" data-ready=\"1\" data-width=\"1280\" data-height=\"720\" data-audit=\"0\"><video data-type=\"2\" width=\"680\" height=\"auto\" data-url=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/rest/app/note/video/3563984?jsondata=%7B%22data_style%22%3A%22jump%22%7D\" class=\"_js_videojs_hls\" data-noneedinit=\"0\" controls=\"\" src=\"blob:https://www.mafengwo.cn/b2672eb1-a061-4aaf-a035-fe0306942c03\"></video></div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n        \r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897876701\" data-seq=\"1897876702\" data-pid=\"1897876701\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1897876701.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/b5/2c/49bac49200503c35fd39a70a324cf07c.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/b5/2c/49bac49200503c35fd39a70a324cf07c.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/b5/2c/49bac49200503c35fd39a70a324cf07c.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897876701\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897977639\" data-seq=\"1897977640\" data-pid=\"1897977639\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1897977639.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/b5/6a/47a5dda34a149c95dfe0aa0f1487e0e8.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/b5/6a/47a5dda34a149c95dfe0aa0f1487e0e8.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/b5/6a/47a5dda34a149c95dfe0aa0f1487e0e8.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897977639\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897977648\" data-seq=\"1897977649\" data-pid=\"1897977648\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1897977648.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 905px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/69/51/d152d6975cbf882a24905e0d9e1a2736.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/69/51/d152d6975cbf882a24905e0d9e1a2736.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/69/51/d152d6975cbf882a24905e0d9e1a2736.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897977648\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897876907\" data-seq=\"1897876908\" data-pid=\"1897876907\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1897876907.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 905px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/e9/f9/ea6ef62d9666364fa5ccfe8ab245844c.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/e9/f9/ea6ef62d9666364fa5ccfe8ab245844c.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/e9/f9/ea6ef62d9666364fa5ccfe8ab245844c.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897876907\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897876912\" data-seq=\"1897876913\" data-pid=\"1897876912\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1897876912.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 905px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/58/6a/7bbba1421e002b8c572333b5d083cadf.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/58/6a/7bbba1421e002b8c572333b5d083cadf.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/58/6a/7bbba1421e002b8c572333b5d083cadf.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897876912\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897876727\" data-seq=\"1897876729\" data-pid=\"1897876727\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1897876727.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/02/4b/81d6bce95b6ebd1b6ac4328d1f7ef6fc.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/02/4b/81d6bce95b6ebd1b6ac4328d1f7ef6fc.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/02/4b/81d6bce95b6ebd1b6ac4328d1f7ef6fc.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897876727\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897977644\" data-seq=\"1897977645\" data-pid=\"1897977644\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1897977644.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/b3/08/d88d45372d0ea78985ea1580d79e7dc6.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/b3/08/d88d45372d0ea78985ea1580d79e7dc6.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/b3/08/d88d45372d0ea78985ea1580d79e7dc6.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897977644\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897867747\">\r\n                                                                            <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10684.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"南京\" target=\"_blank\">南京</a>\r\n                                                                                                            夫子庙<br>\r\n主要由孔庙、学宫、贡院三大建筑群组成。始建于东晋年间，立太学于秦淮\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12967.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"河南\" target=\"_blank\">河南</a>\r\n                                                                                                            岸，移学宫于秦淮\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14407.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"河北\" target=\"_blank\">河北</a>\r\n                                                                                                            ，并在学宫前建庙祭祀孔夫子。四毁五建，最后一次破坏于1937年侵华日寇炮火中，1984年后陆续修葺复建。<br>\r\n老门东，秦淮河风光带，开设金陵刻经、\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10684.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"南京\" target=\"_blank\">南京</a>\r\n                                                                                                            白局、德云社、布画、竹刻、提线木偶等一系列民俗工艺，也有许多\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10684.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"南京\" target=\"_blank\">南京</a>\r\n                                                                                                            地区传统美食小吃。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897981016\" data-seq=\"1897981017\" data-pid=\"1897981016\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1897981016.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/61/0d/4327a363b392ae03c57d4fea73a21471.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/61/0d/4327a363b392ae03c57d4fea73a21471.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/61/0d/4327a363b392ae03c57d4fea73a21471.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897981016\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897981029\" data-seq=\"1897981030\" data-pid=\"1897981029\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1897981029.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/1e/d7/7c286938e0a3ffa421f5626ebe34faaa.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/1e/d7/7c286938e0a3ffa421f5626ebe34faaa.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/1e/d7/7c286938e0a3ffa421f5626ebe34faaa.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897981029\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897981006\" data-seq=\"1897981007\" data-pid=\"1897981006\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1897981006.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/32/ed/6e4fa250550dd2db2ffa6c1689275d00.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/32/ed/6e4fa250550dd2db2ffa6c1689275d00.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/32/ed/6e4fa250550dd2db2ffa6c1689275d00.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897981006\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897981762\">\r\n                                                                                                        可爱的阿姨也是我镜头里的风景啦\r\n                                                                                                        <!-- <img src=\'h\' style=\'width:hpx;\' />-->\r\n                        <img src=\"http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/20@2x.png\">\r\n                                                        </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897981733\" data-seq=\"1897981734\" data-pid=\"1897981733\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1897981733.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1061px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/5e/c5/b83d02beb5ea90abb3c3bc74e9a72ae9.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/5e/c5/b83d02beb5ea90abb3c3bc74e9a72ae9.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/5e/c5/b83d02beb5ea90abb3c3bc74e9a72ae9.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897981733\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div data-seq=\"1897979137\" data-index=\"6\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"t1\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\">江南忆，最忆是秦淮</span></h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897979138\">\r\n                                                                                                        秦淮河，\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10684.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"南京\" target=\"_blank\">南京</a>\r\n                                                                                                            市最大的地区性河流。历史上，其航运、灌溉作用，孕育了\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10684.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"南京\" target=\"_blank\">南京</a>\r\n                                                                                                            古老文明，被称为\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10684.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"南京\" target=\"_blank\">南京</a>\r\n                                                                                                            的母亲河，极富盛名，被称为“\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"中国\" target=\"_blank\">中国</a>\r\n                                                                                                            第一历史文化名河”。<br>\r\n“朱雀桥边野草花，乌衣巷口夕阳斜。”\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897983992\" data-seq=\"1897983993\" data-pid=\"1897983992\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1897983992.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/55/e2/4d95658a460dcfbbbd14413fea736ae5.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/55/e2/4d95658a460dcfbbbd14413fea736ae5.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/55/e2/4d95658a460dcfbbbd14413fea736ae5.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897983992\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n   