         <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898455623\">\r\n                                                                                                        清晚期   象牙镂雕群仙祝寿纹大瓶<br>\r\n此件象牙大瓶器型硕大，盖钮雕刻仕女童子，绕颈一周刻众多仙姑，瓶身满刻亭台楼阁、云彩、树石、人物，组成一幅生动的群仙祝寿画面。雕刻细密谨严，以极繁琐之手法来表现雕琢之能事。此类题材看似表现自由逍遥享乐的神仙世界，其实更象热闹繁华的市井生活。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898355385\" data-seq=\"1898355386\" data-pid=\"1898355385\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898355385.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"height: 905px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/52/54/bbb6e8e63909ab5ac4b81e8dc6339cf3.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/52/54/bbb6e8e63909ab5ac4b81e8dc6339cf3.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898355385\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898356052\">\r\n                                                                                                        清   红木雕苦行僧<br>\r\n用整块红木圆雕出一位正在清修的梵像老者的形象，全身无衣遮体、双目深陷，肌骨嶙峋，作低头冥思状。雕像身体骨骼部位表达明晰，加上打磨功夫细腻温润，使得整个人物立体感很强，如真人一般。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898342857\" data-seq=\"1898355445\" data-pid=\"1898342857\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898342857.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"heigh